### Changeset

<!-- livebook:{"break_markdown":true} -->

If everything is configured correctly, you can now call `for_create/3` to create a changeset.

```elixir
Tutorial.Profile
|> Ash.Changeset.for_create(:create, %{name: "My Name"})
